snippet.title: Strider II. [Mega Drive]. 1CC. EXPERT. No Death. 60Fps.
snippet.description:
Strider II. [Mega Drive]. 1CC. EXPERT. No Death. 60Fps.
:- Played By PiE. - "June 14th, 2020".
.
Sega Retro - "A sequel to Strider, released for the Sega Mega Drive, Sega Master System and the Sega Game Gear in 1993. It should not be confused with the later release of Strider 2 which was developed in-house by Capcom - Strider II was developed by U.S. Gold, who, at the time, had the rights to the Strider license outside of Japan."
.
